edia%2Fzh%2F8%2F83%2FExecutiveDecision_poster.jpg&h=3f3df4c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/1/1d/Conairinternational.jpg/220px-Conairinternational.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fthumb%2F1%2F1d%2FConairinternational.jpg%2F220px-Conairinternational.jpg&h=c2fc6b84&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/fc/Armageddon-poster06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ffc%2FArmageddon-poster06.jpg&h=891e86ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.一架載滿400名乘客的波音747從希臘雅典起飛前往美國華盛頓首府的途中，被一群由阿拉伯人納吉&middot;哈森帶領的恐怖份子挾持，要求美國釋放他們的首腦艾爾&middot;沙耶&middot;亞法，否則將在華盛頓上空引爆機上的毒氣彈，摧毀美國東岸超過四千萬條人命..<br />\n<br />\n2.八年前，自海軍陸戰隊受訓完畢的卡麥倫坡（尼可拉斯凱吉飾）為了保護剛懷孕的妻子免於小混混的騷擾，導致過失殺人被判了十年徒刑。<br />\n在獄中表現良好的他，終於在女兒八歲生日當天獲得假釋，卡麥倫坡希望能親自將生日禮物送到女兒手中，因此要求典獄官讓他登上空中監獄，以節省舟車往返的時間。 但這踏空中監獄正巧搭載一批全美最殘暴兇狠的犯人....<br />\n<br />\n3.地球即將被跟德州一樣大的隕石撞擊，為了毀滅隕石，美國國家航空暨太空總署決定派人在隕石上挖一個洞直到核心，放一顆炸彈在裡面引爆，從內部炸開隕石。布魯斯威力演的史哈利在中國擁有油田，是公認成功的石油大老闆。他並不信任他一個年輕屬下小傑，因此也不爽他女兒蕾跟他交往。<br />\n這時，美國政府來找他了，告訴他隕石的事情，說希望他帶領他的石油工人們，在專業太空人陪伴下，到隕石上挖洞放炸彈<br />\n<br />\n7 25PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1Wipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=493abcb5\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1Wipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=ff03c608\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f16324f4dfa6321606bec74cc6ee4c8d82801f6","tid":1812274,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:10:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f06a04bacfc1be4d21f248795ed912df30a3e89","tid":1812274,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T12:53:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc85d01637441835a4f8ce1923e908d30ceb81bf","tid":1812274,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T13:59:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a49b6ca3036e1488f9d7fd4fe9e4713a541a6bb2","tid":1812274,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T15:22:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"592702ccf974fc87ff31d5dc0314ca5f1adc5fa0","tid":1812274,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T16:34:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}